lmckenzi pushed 8 commits to branch R4B-Lloyd.

  • https://jira.hl7.org/browse/FHIR-19955 - corrected schematrons (24acfad)
  • https://jira.hl7.org/browse/FHIR-26307 Fixed dom-3 expression & schematron (df2409c)
  • https://jira.hl7.org/browse/FHIR-26565 - Adjust global-1 expression and XPath to allow Parameters to be empty (3d8b755)
  • https://jira.hl7.org/browse/FHIR-21180 - Fix XPath to be consistent w/ FHIRPath (d260b8a)
  • https://jira.hl7.org/browse/FHIR-25390 - Correct capitalization of 'boolean' in que-7 (a7c8e37)
  • https://jira.hl7.org/browse/FHIR-29595 - Fixed context invariant typo (0f9f038)
  • https://jira.hl7.org/browse/FHIR-26306, https://jira.hl7.org/browse/FHIR-19968 - Fixed eld-19 and eld-20 to apply to full string, fixed part of escaping issue w/ eld-19 (remainder of 26306 requires a tooling change too) (fa198e5)
  • Updates to vocab from most recent run (bce7cbe)
